dsk2nib
------------------------------------------
Apple II DSK-to-NIB and NIB-to-DSK image file conversion utilities.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/slotek/dsk2nib

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/slotek/dsk2nib.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack dsk2nib-0+git20230318-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./dsk2nib-0+git20230318-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/dsk2nib-0+git20230318-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/dsk2nib-0+git20230318-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(dsk2nib)
  /usr/bin/dsk2nib.exe
  /usr/bin/nib2dsk.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/dsk2nib.README
  /usr/share/doc/dsk2nib/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/dsk2nib/README.md

------------------

